cxxpool is a portable, header-only thread pool for C++


Install
-------

./configure
make install

OR

Copy src/cxxpool.h to your project.


cxxpool is written using C++11 and has no dependencies except for the 
standard library. Supported compilers: g++ (>=4.6), clang++ (>=3.2), icc (>=14)

To build and run the tests the following libraries are required:
- libunittest (http://libunittest.sourceforge.net)

cxxpool is being developed by Christian Blume. Contact Christian at
chr.blume@gmail.com for any questions or comments.
